quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  90,1,I swear by this town
  90,2,as you reside in this town
  90,3,"[and] by the father and him whom he begot"
  90,4,certainly We created man in travail
  90,5,Does he suppose that no one will ever have power over him
  90,6,"He says, ‘I have squandered immense wealth.’"
  90,7,Does he suppose that no one sees him
  90,8,Have We not made for him two eyes
  90,9,"a tongue, and two lips"
  90,10,"and shown him the two paths [of good and evil]"
  90,11,Yet he has not embarked upon the uphill task
  90,12,And what will show you what is the uphill task
  90,13,"[It is] the freeing of a slave"
  90,14,"or feeding, during days of [general] starvation"
  90,15,an orphan among relatives
  90,16,or a needy man in desolation
  90,17,"while being one of those who have faith and enjoin one another to patience, and enjoin one another to compassion"
  90,18,They are the People of the Right Hand
  90,19,"But those who defy Our signs, they are the People of the Left Hand"
  90,20,"A closed Fire will be [imposed] upon them"